[H1]Installation Options:

[H2]Install Driver
  Enable/Disable the inclusion the amdgpu driver as part of the
  installation.

[H2]Start on install
  Enable/Disable starting the amdgpu driver after installation.

[H1]Maintenance:

[H2]Uninstall Driver
  Uninstall runfile-based amdgpu driver installation. This is not
  available for package installed drivers.